[{"node": {"id_": "3deb862f-f34b-419a-b9bb-8be7ea658f25", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "data\\documents\\医疗知识问答.txt", "file_name": "医疗知识问答.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 5426, "creation_date": "2026-03-08", "last_modified_date": "2026-03-08"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "1bf85bbc-6168-4cb4-9ecd-3ac2df28f90b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "data\\documents\\医疗知识问答.txt", "file_name": "医疗知识问答.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 5426, "creation_date": "2026-03-08", "last_modified_date": "2026-03-08"}, "hash": "8fcd66a009a392ab8f4ce99614f9de58bf333b16a85cdbdb531ced33a930e385", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "95dbb901-6834-4f17-a1c8-f6b3258753bd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b93806c8ec7050e2532c11676e6a311e1de5b1f9708cb978bee32d1136b6cd08", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "# 医疗知识问答数据\n\n## 一、高血压相关\n\n### 高血压的诊断标准\n高血压的诊断标准是指在未使用降压药物的情况下，非同日3次测量血压，收缩压≥140mmHg和/或舒张压≥90mmHg即可诊断为高血压。\n\n### 高血压的症状\n高血压的常见症状包括：头痛、头晕、耳鸣、眼花、心悸、气短、乏力等。部分患者可能没有任何症状，仅在体检时发现血压升高。\n\n### 高血压的治疗方法\n1. 生活方式干预：低盐饮食、戒烟限酒、适度运动、控制体重\n2. 药物治疗：常用降压药包括利尿剂、β受体阻滞剂、钙通道阻滞剂、血管紧张素转换酶抑制剂、血管紧张素II受体拮抗剂等\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 280, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "score": 0.5246002613402871, "class_name": "NodeWithScore"}, {"node": {"id_": "95dbb901-6834-4f17-a1c8-f6b3258753bd", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "data\\documents\\医疗知识问答.txt", "file_name": "医疗知识问答.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 5426, "creation_date": "2026-03-08", "last_modified_date": "2026-03-08"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "1bf85bbc-6168-4cb4-9ecd-3ac2df28f90b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "data\\documents\\医疗知识问答.txt", "file_name": "医疗知识问答.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 5426, "creation_date": "2026-03-08", "last_modified_date": "2026-03-08"}, "hash": "8fcd66a009a392ab8f4ce99614f9de58bf333b16a85cdbdb531ced33a930e385", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "3deb862f-f34b-419a-b9bb-8be7ea658f25", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "data\\documents\\医疗知识问答.txt", "file_name": "医疗知识问答.txt", "file_type": "text/plain", "file_size": 5426, "creation_date": "2026-03-08", "last_modified_date": "2026-03-08"}, "hash": "1c134a8e1a13a7105a8df85be95e224bf8d4c3c92e9d9a57dcda851cbfaf80e8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1314a280-2efb-4a7c-bc96-eb5bc2122680", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "07fc2b4c8ec5250e91c8356ae4cf64b22dfc3154366295785010b41defefcc2b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "定期监测血压，遵医嘱用药\n\n### 高血压患者饮食建议\n- 控制钠盐摄入，每日不超过6克\n- 增加钾的摄入，多吃新鲜蔬菜水果\n- 限制脂肪摄入，少吃动物内脏\n- 适量摄入蛋白质\n- 戒烟限酒\n\n---\n\n## 二、糖尿病相关\n\n### 糖尿病的诊断标准\n糖尿病的诊断标准为空腹血糖≥7.0mmol/L，或餐后2小时血糖≥11.1mmol/L，或随机血糖≥11.1mmol/L伴有糖尿病症状。\n\n### 糖尿病的常见症状\n多饮、多尿、多食、体重下降是糖尿病的典型症状。其他症状包括：乏力、视力模糊、皮肤瘙痒、反复感染等。\n\n### 糖尿病的饮食控制\n1. 控制总热量摄入\n2. 均衡营养，碳水化合物、蛋白质、脂肪合理搭配\n3. 选择低GI（血糖生成指数）食物\n4. 定时定量进餐\n5.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 281, "end_char_idx": 622, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "score": 0.45350117535929224, "class_name": "NodeWithScore"}, {"node": {"id_": "1ea21465-483b-4321-aa0d-a8ee1e82dc55", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "