唤\n2. 呼叫急救：拨打120\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1625, "end_char_idx": 2110, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "score": 0.33918400861150033, "class_name": "NodeWithScore"}]